Let’s be real — looking “effortless” actually means being high maintenance. There’s a LOT of prep work every "clean girl" does behind the scenes. But here’s the secret: once you set up the right habits, your everyday routine can BECOME low maintenance and easier than ever.

These are the 10 high maintenance beauty habits that will *secretly* make you look low maintenance. (But tbh, these habits aren't even that time consuming -- maybe 5-10 minutes MAX). These are the little things I do that save me time, make me feel put-together, and keep me from crashing out on the days I’m tired, stressed, or running late.
